SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: IIEF01-Able to Penetrate Your Partner;IIEF01-Penetration Ability
SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: International Index of Erectile Function - Over the past four weeks when you attempted sexual intercourse, how often were you able to penetrate (enter) your partner?

SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: International Index of Erectile Function - Over the past four weeks how do you rate your confidence that you could get and keep an erection?

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: IIEF01-Did You Have Feeling of Orgasm;IIEF01-Orgasm Frequency

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: IIEF01-Desire Frequency;IIEF01-Have You Felt Sexual Desire

SKOS_CONCEPT.alt_label: IIEF01-Ejaculation Frequency;IIEF01-How Often Did You Ejaculate

SKOS_CONCEPT.definition: International Index of Erectile Function - Over the past four weeks how many times have you attempted sexual intercourse?
